import React from 'react'
import { Typography, AppBar, Toolbar, CssBaseline } from '@mui/material'

const Header = () => {
  return (
      <CssBaseline>
        <AppBar position='relative'>
          <Toolbar>
            <Typography variant='h1'>Daniel's Translator Web App</Typography>
          </Toolbar>
        </AppBar>
      </CssBaseline>
  )
}

export default Header
